# Keep Docker build context small.
# The installer and config are the only files needed at image-build time.
# Everything else is mounted at run time via -v.
# Credential files (.amd_user / .amd_pass) are NOT copied into the image —
# they are passed as BuildKit --secret mounts and never touch a layer.
*
!docker/FPGAs_AdaptiveSoCs_Unified_*.bin
!docker/Xilinx_Unified_*.bin
!docker/install_config.txt
